caption: Just want to say how proud i am for jack Johnson and jack gillinksy? their life's have changed so much in the past couple years now. They haven't become famous by luck, they are what they are now is because they where motivated enough to work hard for their dreams to come true no matter what! That's what I respect the most the fact that they stood out and didn't care what anybody thinks and accomplished their dreams no matter what! So thank you boys you really have inspired me?
